                <h2 class="element-invisible">You are here</h2><div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/renison/">Renison University College</a> » <a href="/renison/facilities-services">Facilities and services</a> » <a href="/renison/lusi-wong-library">Lusi Wong Library</a> » </div>        <h1>Library Hours</h1>
    <div class="node-tabs"></div>        <div id="content">
        <div class="region region-content">
    <div id="block-system-main" class="block block-system block-odd">

    
  <div class="content">
    <div id="node-115" class="node node-uw-web-page node-even"  about="/renison/lusi-wong-library/library-hours" typeof="foaf:Document">
  <div class="node-inner">

    
    
    
    <div class="content_node">
      <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded"><h2><b>Fall and Winter terms  </b></h2>

<p>Monday to Thursday – 8:30 a.m. to 10:00 p.m. <br />
	Friday – 8:30 a.m. to 4:00 p.m. <br />
	Saturday – 1:00 p.m. to 5:00 p.m. <br />
	Sunday – 1:00 p.m. to 4:00 p.m. </p>

<h2><strong>Spring/Summer term</strong></h2>

<p>Monday to Thursday – 8:30 a.m. to 8:30 p.m. <br />
	Friday – 8:30 a.m. to 4:00 p.m.<br />
	Closed Saturday and Sunday</p>
